  "text": "Excuse me sir question for you. How old were you when you became a millionaire? I was 20, 21, 21 years old. And how'd you get rich? God made me a millionaire. God made you a millionaire. Who is your God? Jesus Christ, my Lord and Savior. And what's your name? My name is James Winston. And what do you do? My quarterback. You're an NFL player? Yes, I am. Could I get a minute with you real quick? Yeah, of course. What was the most amount of money that you made in a single year? 20, 25 million actually. 25 million dollars. Did you come from a lot of money? No, I didn't. You did come from money? No, I didn't. You didn't come from a rich family, but a rich family is going to come from you. A wealthy family is going to come from me, three generations behind me, through the choices and decisions that we make. Hey, generational wealth, baby. Absolutely, baby. I mean, a lot of athletes go broke. What did you do with that money when you first started to make it? I didn't really touch my game money. I really worked off my endorsement money. How did you develop that mindset to think so much bigger? Gratitude is the key to abundance. My dad, he told me like the three rules of life. And that's God, that's education. And you can do anything you put your mind to. And the three rules of football was never give up, never give up, never give up. How do you know? I'm 32. Somebody doesn't believe in God. What would your message be to them? My message would be find a local church. You have a creator. You have someone that loves you dearly. Jesus Christ died on the cross for us, and he saved us for our sins. I like that you're not afraid to say that either. A lot of people just say, God, but who is your God? Well, we're called to be bold for his throne, so he can then vouch for us to get into heaven. I love that. These worldly things, they're here. These trees and stuff, they're going to be here for a good while. But we are only here for a vapor. So how can you be an influence? How can you impact someone else to serve a high calling on this earth? This is a vital study that the people need right now. It's simple things, man. It is bigger than you. And I think when you understand that you have a creator that puts you here for a very unique purpose, I just let my life shine, and I let his life shine through me. Can I tell you something? What's up, Joe? That was a beautiful interview, man. I appreciate it. Thank you so much for your time. I connect with all the millionaires and billionaires out there. Can I get your contact? Yeah, absolutely. You can get my contact.",
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.3,
      "text": "Excuse me sir question for you. How old were you when you became a millionaire?"
    },
    {
      "start": 3.7,
      "end": 6.4,
      "text": "I was 20, 21, 21 years old. And how'd you get rich?"
    },
    {
      "start": 6.7,
      "end": 7.6,
      "text": "God made me a millionaire."
    },
    {
      "start": 7.9,
      "end": 9.3,
      "text": "God made you a millionaire. Who is your God?"
    },
    {
      "start": 9.5,
      "end": 10.9,
      "text": "Jesus Christ, my Lord and Savior."
    },
    {
      "start": 11.1,
      "end": 11.6,
      "text": "And what's your name?"
    },
    {
      "start": 11.8,
      "end": 12.7,
      "text": "My name is James Winston."
    },
    {
      "start": 12.9,
      "end": 13.4,
      "text": "And what do you do?"
    },
    {
      "start": 13.6,
      "end": 14.1,
      "text": "My quarterback."
    },
    {
      "start": 14.4,
      "end": 15.1,
      "text": "You're an NFL player?"
    },
    {
      "start": 15.3,
      "end": 15.9,
      "text": "Yes, I am."
    },
    {
      "start": 16.0,
      "end": 17.0,
      "text": "Could I get a minute with you real quick?"
    },
    {
      "start": 17.2,
      "end": 17.6,
      "text": "Yeah, of course."
    },
    {
      "start": 17.8,
      "end": 20.0,
      "text": "What was the most amount of money that you made in a single year?"
    },
    {
      "start": 20.1,
      "end": 21.7,
      "text": "20, 25 million actually."
    },
    {
      "start": 21.9,
      "end": 22.7,
      "text": "25 million dollars."
    },
    {
      "start": 23.0,
      "end": 23.8,
      "text": "Did you come from a lot of money?"
    },
    {
      "start": 24.1,
      "end": 24.7,
      "text": "No, I didn't."
    },
    {
      "start": 24.8,
      "end": 25.6,
      "text": "You did come from money?"
    },
    {
      "start": 25.7,
      "end": 26.2,
      "text": "No, I didn't."
    },
    {
      "start": 26.2,
      "end": 28.5,
      "text": "You didn't come from a rich family, but a rich family is going to come from you."
    },
    {
      "start": 28.5,
      "end": 32.5,
      "text": "A wealthy family is going to come from me, three generations behind me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 32.5,
      "end": 34.5,
      "text": "through the choices and decisions that we make."
    },
    {
      "start": 34.6,
      "end": 35.7,
      "text": "Hey, generational wealth, baby."
    },
    {
      "start": 35.8,
      "end": 36.5,
      "text": "Absolutely, baby."
    },
    {
      "start": 36.7,
      "end": 37.8,
      "text": "I mean, a lot of athletes go broke."
    },
    {
      "start": 37.9,
      "end": 39.8,
      "text": "What did you do with that money when you first started to make it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.8,
      "end": 41.3,
      "text": "I didn't really touch my game money."
    },
    {
      "start": 41.4,
      "end": 43.1,
      "text": "I really worked off my endorsement money."
    },
    {
      "start": 43.3,
      "end": 45.5,
      "text": "How did you develop that mindset to think so much bigger?"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.7,
      "end": 47.5,
      "text": "Gratitude is the key to abundance."
    },
    {
      "start": 47.8,
      "end": 49.8,
      "text": "My dad, he told me like the three rules of life."
    },
    {
      "start": 50.0,
      "end": 51.2,
      "text": "And that's God, that's education."
    },
    {
      "start": 51.5,
      "end": 53.2,
      "text": "And you can do anything you put your mind to."
    },
    {
      "start": 53.4,
      "end": 56.1,
      "text": "And the three rules of football was never give up, never give up, never give up."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.2,
      "end": 56.7,
      "text": "How do you know?"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.9,
      "end": 57.2,
      "text": "I'm 32."
    },
    {
      "start": 57.2,
      "end": 58.6,
      "text": "Somebody doesn't believe in God."
    },
    {
      "start": 58.7,
      "end": 59.6,
      "text": "What would your message be to them?"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.9,
      "end": 61.9,
      "text": "My message would be find a local church."
    },
    {
      "start": 62.1,
      "end": 62.8,
      "text": "You have a creator."
    },
    {
      "start": 63.1,
      "end": 65.4,
      "text": "You have someone that loves you dearly."
    },
    {
      "start": 65.5,
      "end": 68.9,
      "text": "Jesus Christ died on the cross for us, and he saved us for our sins."
    },
    {
      "start": 69.1,
      "end": 70.4,
      "text": "I like that you're not afraid to say that either."
    },
    {
      "start": 70.7,
      "end": 72.0,
      "text": "A lot of people just say, God, but who is your God?"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.1,
      "end": 73.8,
      "text": "Well, we're called to be bold for his throne,"
    },
    {
      "start": 73.9,
      "end": 76.2,
      "text": "so he can then vouch for us to get into heaven."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.4,
      "end": 76.8,
      "text": "I love that."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.8,
      "end": 78.7,
      "text": "These worldly things, they're here."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.9,
      "end": 81.3,
      "text": "These trees and stuff, they're going to be here for a good while."
    },
    {
      "start": 81.4,
      "end": 83.1,
      "text": "But we are only here for a vapor."
    },
    {
      "start": 83.3,
      "end": 85.0,
      "text": "So how can you be an influence?"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.0,
      "end": 89.0,
      "text": "How can you impact someone else to serve a high calling on this earth?"
    },
    {
      "start": 89.1,
      "end": 91.2,
      "text": "This is a vital study that the people need right now."
    },
    {
      "start": 92.3,
      "end": 93.6,
      "text": "It's simple things, man."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.7,
      "end": 94.9,
      "text": "It is bigger than you."
    },
    {
      "start": 95.2,
      "end": 97.3,
      "text": "And I think when you understand that you have a creator"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.3,
      "end": 99.4,
      "text": "that puts you here for a very unique purpose,"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.6,
      "end": 102.3,
      "text": "I just let my life shine, and I let his life shine through me."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.5,
      "end": 103.1,
      "text": "Can I tell you something?"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.3,
      "end": 103.7,
      "text": "What's up, Joe?"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.8,
      "end": 104.8,
      "text": "That was a beautiful interview, man."
    },
    {
      "start": 105.0,
      "end": 105.5,
      "text": "I appreciate it."
    },
    {
      "start": 105.5,
      "end": 106.6,
      "text": "Thank you so much for your time."
    },
    {
      "start": 106.9,
      "end": 108.8,
      "text": "I connect with all the millionaires and billionaires out there."
    },
    {
      "start": 108.9,
      "end": 109.6,
      "text": "Can I get your contact?"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.7,
      "end": 110.2,
      "text": "Yeah, absolutely."
    },
    {
      "start": 110.4,
      "end": 110.9,
      "text": "You can get my contact."
    }
  ],
